Output obsidian-save.gif
Output obsidian-save.mp4

Set FontSize 15
Set Width 1000
Set Height 600
Set Padding 16
Set TypingSpeed 30ms
Set Theme "Catppuccin Mocha"

Hide
Type `cd /tmp/MyVault && export OBSIDIAN_VAULT_PATH=/tmp/MyVault && clear`
Enter
Sleep 1s
Show

