Enter
Type `#  pipeline. Decided: demos render from committed vhs tapes. Kickoff Tuesday."`
Enter
Sleep 1s

Type `claude --continue -p --permission-mode acceptEdits "/obsidian-save"`
Sleep 500ms
Enter
Hide
Wait@300s
Show
Sleep 5s

Type "ls People Projects Daily"
Sleep 500ms
Enter
Sleep 3s

Type `head -28 "People/Grace Hopper.md"`
Sleep 500ms
Enter
Sleep 9s

Sleep 5s
